      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Antibodies to p53 and HER-2/neu were evaluated using a cell-based assay. For analysis of HER-2/neu antibody immunity, 96-well microtiter plates (Dynex Technologies, Inc, Chantilly, VA) were coated with 520C9, a monoclonal antibody specific to HER-2/neu, and diluted to a concentration of 10 g/mL with carbonate buffer."
